==English==

===Noun===
'''silica group'''
# {{mineralogy}} A large group of [[silicate]] [[mineral]]s having a [[silicon]] to [[oxygen]] ratio of '''1:2'''. This group includes many silicates of [[sodium]], [[potassium]], [[calcium]], and [[aluminum]] in an open network structure. 

